data.body:
Added a French translation of the `README.md` file as `README_fr.md` inside the `i18n` folder. This will help French-speaking users to better understand the project.

Hopefully other people will translate the `README.md` into different languages and put their versions in the same folder.

I also added a section to the original `README.md` file to be able to easily switch the language
